description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 10, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 30, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Stringalong for East, Leverage for South, and 2 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [30 Votes, Common]
